commit message: Bring german translation up to date
Added Dutch translations translation thanks to mapleleaf, bartwesselink and rick-bakker.
Added flag for the Frankfurt region

Fix DNS record editing

Fixes #39

When a record is edited the recordTypeSpinner should be moved to the
matching record type.  In order to refer to the values by position index
we need to ensure the order of the values.  Since a HashMap does not
ensure the order of the values, the position of the 'A' record for
instance is not predictable.  By converting to a LinkedHashMap the order
is ensured and we can set the selection by position.
Add a droplet spinner for easier editing of A records
Fixes #9 (marks synchronising notifications as ongoing for persistence until success)
Fixes #31 (shows a Toast notification when a synchronisation fails)
Updated to work with the newest version of gradle. and updated dependencies
Added the flag for Toronto region
Fixed creating droplet with ssh keys. fixes #36
